(4230, '2007-06-18', 'Race: Caterham Expansion Pack Available For Free', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_1087\" style=\"display: none;\">
<p>For one week only, June 18 - 22, current owners of <a href=\"index.php?area=game&amp;AppId=4230\"><i>RACE – The WTCC Game</i></a> can receive the new Catherham Expansion pack for free. RACE owners will receive the offer when they launch Steam. <br/><br/>From acclaimed Swedish developers SimBin, RACE is the first title to deliver the intense action of the WTCC championship to PC gamers. The CATERHAM Expansion includes a wealth of new features: <br/>•	Three car models from Caterham Cars Limited in 60 different designs<br/>•	Two new tracks, Imola and Estoril<br/>•	Performance improvements for tracks and cars<br/>•	Upgraded options and settings for more customizable game configurations<br/>•	A new Performance Monitor that determines the best possible graphics settings<br/>•	A new controller interface for joy-pads and keyboard/mouse controls<br/><br/>Starting June 22, <a href=\"index.php?area=game&amp;AppId=4290\"><i>RACE: CATERHAM</i></a> will be available on Steam for $4.95. RACE + the CATERHAM Expansion will be available for $24.95.</p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
</div>'),
(4230, '2007-06-22', 'Race: Caterham Expansion Pack Now Available', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_1102\" style=\"display: none;\">
<p><a href=\"http://storefront.steampowered.com/v/index.php?area=game&amp;AppId=4290\"><i>RACE: CATERHAM</i></a>, the official expansion pack for RACE - The WTCC Game, is now available for just $4.95. If you\'re new to the racing series, pick up <a href=\"http://storefront.steampowered.com/v/index.php?area=package&amp;SubId=379\"><i>RACE + the CATHERHAM expansion pack</i></a> for just $24.95.</p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
</div>'),
(4230, '2007-10-15', 'Now On Steam - Race 07 - The Official Wtcc Game', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_1252\" style=\"display: ;\">
<p><a href=\"http://storefront.steampowered.com/v/index.php?area=game&amp;AppId=8600\">RACE 07 - The Official WTCC Game</a> is now available worldwide via Steam.<br/><br/>RACE 07 - The Official WTCC Game features the full FIA WTCC season of 2007 including all cars and tracks, as well as several new support classes and tracks from all over the world. The game also features the full WTCC season of 2006 which was included in the games predecessor RACE – The WTCC Game, released in 2006 on PC. <br/><br/>For a taste of the exhilarating multiplayer race action and new Formula cars, <a href=\"http://storefront.steampowered.com/v/index.php?area=game&amp;AppId=4260\">play the RACE 07 demo</a>.</p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
</div>');
